39.body:
在 $O(\log n)$ 的时间内计算 $$ \sum_{x=0}^n \left\lfloor \frac{ax + b}{c} \right\rfloor $$ // @description 类欧几里得算法 ll floor_sum(ll a, ll b, ll c, ll n) { ll m = (a * n + b) / c, S1 = n * (n + 1) / 2; if (a == 0) { return b / c * (n + 1); } else if (a >= c || b >= c) { ll f = S1 * (a / c) + b / c * (n + 1); return f + floor_sum(a % c, b % c, c, n); } else { return m * n - floor_sum(c, c - b - 1, a, m - 1); }
}

ll kruskal(int n) { std::sort(G.begin(), G.end(), [](Edge a, Edge b) { return get<2>(a) < get<2>(b); }); ll ans = 0, cnt = 0; DSU dsu(n + 1); for (auto [u, v, w] : G) { if (dsu.find(u) == dsu.find(v)) { continue; } ans += w, cnt++; dsu.merge(u, v); if (cnt == n - 1) { return ans; } } return -1;
}

// @description 朴素并查集 struct DSU { vector<int> fa; DSU(int n) : fa(n) { for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) fa[i] = i; } int find(int x) { return fa[x] == x ? x : fa[x] = find(fa[x]); } bool same(int x, int y) { return find(x) == find(y); } void merge(int x, int y) { x = find(x), y = find(y); fa[x] = y; }
};

75.body:
// @description 带权并查集 struct DSU { vector<int> fa, sz; DSU(int n) : fa(n), sz(n, 1) { for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) fa[i] = i; } int find(int x) { return fa[x] == x ? x : fa[x] = find(fa[x]); } bool same(int x, int y) { return find(x) == find(y); } int size(int x) { return sz[find(x)]; } void merge(int x, int y) { x = find(x), y = find(y); if (x == y) return; if (sz[x] > sz[y]) swap(x, y); sz[y] += sz[x], fa[x] = y; sz[x] = 0; }
};
